newsitem.title: USA: U.S. stock index futures remain up, but off highs.
newsitem.headline: U.S. stock index futures remain up, but off highs.

text.p: Sept 6 - U.S. stock index futures remained up, but were backed off highs. Sept S&Ps climbed to 659.60 on moderate volume. Estimated volume for Sept was roughly 52,000 and traders saw few major buyers towards the highs. Resistance is at 660.00. -Derivatives Desk(312)408-8750/E-mail:derivatives@reuters.com
